channel.title: Linux problem?
channel.description:
Well I moved my computer from downstairs to upstairs, from wire connected to wireless. I host a webserver on it and everytime I try to access it through my domain I get.
The server at URL is taking too long to respond.
It worked fine downstairs on wired, and the connection on is still 4 bars. ( 1mb + upload) I never had troubles with my windows laptop. Anyone have an explanation? Or could help?
Thanks in advance.
